text:
Grand Central Parkway, east from 31st Street, showing the newly-erected highway emerging from underneath 31st Street. On the right is Astoria Boulevard, and in the background the Long Island Railroad elevated structure. The two views are from the I.R.T. "El" station on 31st Street.

P. L. Sperr

June 24, 1937
Views 1,2:
